title: Patriots Coach Bill Belichick Focused Only On Super Bowl, Not Retirement | NESN Sports Today | NESN.com
text:
by NESN Staff on Thu, Feb 2, 2017 at 11:43PM 1,405 Tweet 
The New England Patriots will aim for a fifth Super Bowl title Sunday when they take on the Atlanta Falcons at NRG Stadium in Houston. 
Patriots head coach Bill Belichick already has accomplished everything as an NFL coach, but retirement is far from his focus this week.
